{"title":"Android开发：Application类的使用","uid":"a27b716432c68fc9a325f5eacf458d34","slug":"Android-Application","date":"2020-04-16T02:19:18.000Z","updated":"2020-05-08T01:40:13.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Android-Application.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h2 id=\"Application类的简介\"><a href=\"#Application类的简介\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Application类的简介\"></a>Application类的简介</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>Application类是维护应用全局状态的基类，Android会在启动应用进程时，创建一个Application对象，且只有一个，即 Application类 是单例模式（singleton）类，不同的组件（如Activity、Service）都可获得Application对象且都是同一个对象</p></blockquote>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h2 id=\"创建自定义的Application类\"><a href=\"#创建自定义的Application类\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"创建自定义的Application类\"></a>创建自定义的Application类</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>我们可以拓展Application类，让Android系统使用我们自定义的Application类来创建Application对象</p></blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>创建Application子类<pre class=\"line-numbers language-java\" data-language=\"java\"><code class=\"language-java\">public class MyApplication extends Application &#123;\n    @Override\n    public void onCreate() &#123;\n        super.onCreate();\n    &#125;\n\n    @Override\n    public void onTerminate() &#123;\n        super.onTerminate();\n    &#125;\n\n    @Override\n    public void onConfigurationChanged(@NonNull Configuration newConfig) &#123;\n        super.onConfigurationChanged(newConfig);\n    &#125;\n\n    @Override\n    public void onLowMemory() &#123;\n        super.onLowMemory();\n    &#125;\n\n    @Override\n    public void onTrimMemory(int level) &#123;\n        super.onTrimMemory(level);\n    &#125;\n&#125;\n</code></pre></li>\n<li>在AndroidManifest.xml中为Application标签添加name属性<pre class=\"line-numbers language-xml\" data-language=\"xml\"><code class=\"language-xml\">&lt;?xml version&#x3D;&quot;1.0&quot; encoding&#x3D;&quot;utf-8&quot;?&gt;\n&lt;manifest xmlns:android&#x3D;&quot;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;schemas.android.com&#x2F;apk&#x2F;res&#x2F;android&quot;\n        package&#x3D;&quot;com.cjpnice.application&quot;&gt;\n\n    &lt;application\n            android:name&#x3D;&quot;.MyApplication&quot;\n            android:allowBackup&#x3D;&quot;true&quot;\n            android:icon&#x3D;&quot;@mipmap&#x2F;ic_launcher&quot;\n            android:label&#x3D;&quot;@string&#x2F;app_name&quot;\n            android:roundIcon&#x3D;&quot;@mipmap&#x2F;ic_launcher_round&quot;\n            android:supportsRtl&#x3D;&quot;true&quot;\n            android:theme&#x3D;&quot;@style&#x2F;AppTheme&quot;&gt;\n        &lt;activity android:name&#x3D;&quot;.MainActivity&quot;&gt;\n            &lt;intent-filter&gt;\n                &lt;action android:name&#x3D;&quot;android.intent.action.MAIN&quot; &#x2F;&gt;\n\n                &lt;category android:name&#x3D;&quot;android.intent.category.LAUNCHER&quot; &#x2F;&gt;\n            &lt;&#x2F;intent-filter&gt;\n        &lt;&#x2F;activity&gt;\n    &lt;&#x2F;application&gt;\n\n&lt;&#x2F;manifest&gt;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"Application生命周期\"><a href=\"#Application生命周期\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Application生命周期\"></a>Application生命周期</h2><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200416104238.png\" alt=\"Application生命周期\"></li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>onCreate():Application创建的时候调用</li>\n<li>onConfigurationChanged(Configuration newConfig):当配置信息改变的时候会调用，如屏幕旋转、语言切换时。</li>\n<li>onLowMemory():Android系统整体内存较低时候调用，通常在这里释放一些不重要的资源，或者提醒用户清一下垃圾，来保证内存足够而让APP进程不被系统杀掉。它和OnTrimMemory中的TRIM_MEMORY_COMPLETE级别相同。</li>\n<li>onTrimMemory(int level)：Android 4.0 之后提供的一个API，用于取代onLowMemory()。在系统内存不足的时会被调用，提示开发者清理部分资源来释放内存，从而避免被 Android 系统杀死。</li>\n<li>onTerminate():Application结束的时候会调用,由系统决定调用的时机</li>\n</ul>\n","text":"Application类的简介 Application类是维护应用全局状态的基类，Android会在启动应用进程时，创建一个Application对象，且只有一个，即 Application类 是单例模式（singleton）类，不同的组件（如Activity、Service）都...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.5k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Android","slug":"Android","count":16,"path":"api/categories/Android.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","count":25,"path":"api/tags/Java.json"},{"name":"Android","slug":"Android","count":16,"path":"api/tags/Android.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Application%E7%B1%BB%E7%9A%84%E7%AE%80%E4%BB%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Application类的简介</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E7%9A%84Application%E7%B1%BB\"><span class=\"toc-text\">创建自定义的Application类</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Application%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%9F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Application生命周期</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"CHEN","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109161140460.jpg","link":"/","description":"学无止境","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/cjpnice","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"Android开发：SharePreference及Sqlite的使用","uid":"9dda3d179906595801d5702aab50132b","slug":"Android-SharePreference","date":"2020-04-16T03:40:26.000Z","updated":"2020-05-08T01:40:59.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Android-SharePreference.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"SharePreferenceSharePreference的作用 SharePreference主要用于保存一些数据在本地的xml文件中, SharePreference的使用写入数据 获取SharedPreferences对象 获取Editor对象 存储信息 提交操作(app...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"4.4k","symbolsTime":"4 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Android","slug":"Android","count":16,"path":"api/categories/Android.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Java","slug":"Java","count":25,"path":"api/tags/Java.json"},{"name":"Android","slug":"Android","count":16,"path":"api/tags/Android.json"}],"author":{"name":"CHEN","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109161140460.jpg","link":"/","description":"学无止境","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/cjpnice","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}}},"next_post":{"title":"Java设计模式：策略模式","uid":"2fcc47af7e967abfb1d26d14cdced0c8","slug":"Java-DesignPattern8","date":"2020-04-16T00:14:53.000Z","updated":"2020-05-08T01:41:30.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Java-DesignPattern8.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"什么是策略模式 Strategy模式也叫策略模式是行为模式之一，它对一系列的算法加以封装，为所有算法定义一个抽象的算法接口，并通过继承该抽象算法接口对所有的算法加以封装和实现，具体的算法选择交由客户端决定（策略）。Strategy模式主要用来平滑地处理算法的切换 。 实现步骤 新...","link":"","photo